Get state names from any type of FIPS codes

Source: R/fips_x_from_y.R
fips2statename.Rd

Get state names from any type of FIPS codes

fips2statename(fips)

Arguments

fips

vector of FIPS

Value

vector of state names

Examples

  cbind(fips_lead_zero(1:80), fips2state_abbrev(1:80), fips2statename(1:80))
